commentary: Ashwin to Pietersen, OUT what a catch! Pietersen bent down low to slog sweep, connecting well and then standing to admire the shot ... only for Manoj Tiwary to come charging across from midwicket before diving full length and clutching the ball with both hands while airborne. But hello, what's this? Pietersen has been stopped at the boundary's edge. Are they checking for the no-ball? It's totally fine, and Pietersen's got to go!
